#. <section class="sutta" id="sn5.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhunīvagga"
msgstr "1. Nuns"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn5.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Uppalavaṇṇāsutta"
msgstr "5. With Uppalavaṇṇā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.288"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn5.5:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā … pe …"
msgstr "Then the nun Uppalavaṇṇā robed up in the morning …"

msgctxt "sn5.5:1.3"
msgid "aññatarasmiṃ supupphitasālarukkhamūle aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr "and stood at the root of a sal tree in full flower."

msgctxt "sn5.5:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ "
"lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo yena uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā uppalavaṇṇaṃ bhikkhuniṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, wanting to make the nun Uppalavaṇṇā feel fear, terror, "
"and goosebumps, wanting to make her fall away from immersion, went up to "
"her and addressed her in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.1"
msgid "“Supupphitaggaṃ upagamma bhikkhuni,"
msgstr "“You’ve come to this sal tree all crowned with flowers"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.2"
msgid "Ekā tuvaṃ tiṭṭhasi sālamūle;"
msgstr "and stand at its root all alone, O nun."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.3"
msgid "Na catthi te dutiyā vaṇṇadhātu,"
msgstr "Your beauty is second to none;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:2.4"
msgid "Bāle na tvaṃ bhāyasi dhuttakānan”ti."
msgstr "silly girl, aren’t you afraid of rascals?”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.132"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.289"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then the nun Uppalavaṇṇā thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.2"
msgid "“ko nu khvāyaṃ manusso vā amanusso vā gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Who’s speaking this verse, a human or a non-human?”"

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho uppalavaṇṇāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then she thought:"

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.4"
msgid ""
"“māro kho ayaṃ pāpimā mama bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo "
"samādhimhā cāvetukāmo gāthaṃ bhāsatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“This is Māra the Wicked, wanting to make me feel fear, terror, and "
"goosebumps, wanting to make me fall away from immersion!”"

msgctxt "sn5.5:3.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī “māro ayaṃ pāpimā” iti viditvā māraṃ "
"pāpimantaṃ gāthāhi paccabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Uppalavaṇṇā, knowing that this was Māra the Wicked, replied to him in "
"verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.1"
msgid "“Sataṃ sahassānipi dhuttakānaṃ,"
msgstr "“Even if 100,000 rascals like you"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.2"
msgid "Idhāgatā tādisakā bhaveyyuṃ;"
msgstr "were to come here,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.3"
msgid "Lomaṃ na iñjāmi na santasāmi,"
msgstr "I’d stir not a hair nor be alarmed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:4.4"
msgid "Na māra bhāyāmi tamekikāpi."
msgstr "I’m not scared of you, Māra, even alone."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.1"
msgid "Esā antaradhāyāmi,"
msgstr "I’ll vanish,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.2"
msgid "kucchiṃ vā pavisāmi te;"
msgstr "or I’ll enter your belly;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.3"
msgid "Pakhumantarikāyampi,"
msgstr "I could stand between your eyebrows"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:5.4"
msgid "tiṭṭhantiṃ maṃ na dakkhasi."
msgstr "and you still wouldn’t see me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.1"
msgid "Cittasmiṃ vasībhūtāmhi,"
msgstr "I’m the master of my own mind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.2"
msgid "iddhipādā subhāvitā;"
msgstr "I’ve developed the bases of psychic power well."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.3"
msgid "Sabbabandhanamuttāmhi,"
msgstr "I’m free from all bonds,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn5.5:6.4"
msgid "na taṃ bhāyāmi āvuso”ti."
msgstr "and I’m not afraid of you, sir!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.290"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn5.5:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ uppalavaṇṇā bhikkhunī”ti dukkhī dummano "
"tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The nun Uppalavaṇṇā knows me!” miserable "
"and sad, vanished right there."
